snippet.title: TRET | Steam Teaser | indie.io
snippet.description:
Wishlist TRET now on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2492610/TRET/

A hybrid puzzler set in a synthwave world. Complex platforming meets physics-based synthball manipulation, with a dash of high-speed races across a neon-soaked landscape, all set to the tune of a killer electronic soundtrack paying homage to the colorful eighties.
